    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/security/simple-oauth2/#use-the-form-data",
    "section_text": "Now, get the user data from the (fake) database, using the username from the form field.\n\nIf there is no such user, we return an error saying \"Incorrect username or password\".\n\nFor the error, we use the exception HTTPException :",
