    "node_kind": "heading",
    "heading_text": "Recap",
    "anchor_id": "recap",
    "section_url": "https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/tutorial/security/simple-oauth2/#recap",
    "section_text": "You now have the tools to implement a complete security system based on username and password for your API.\n\nUsing these tools, you can make the security system compatible with any database and with any user or data model.\n\nThe only detail missing is that it is not actually \"secure\" yet.\n\nIn the next chapter you'll see how to use a secure password hashing library and JWT tokens.",
    "section_inline_code": [
      "username",
      "password"
    ],
